## Requirements
```
scikit-learn
numpy
nltk
```
If not already installed, run `pip install -r requirements.txt`.

## Authorship Attribution Through Classification (needs data in `C50/`)
```
python textVectorizer.py C50/ matrix.npy ground_truth.csv [--stemming] [--stopwords]

```

## Authorship Attribution Through Clustering (needs data in `C50/`)
```
python textVectorizer.py C50/ matrix.npy ground_truth.csv [--stemming] [--stopwords]
python KMeansAuthorship.py matrix.npy kmeans.out 5 [--n_init (int)] [--max_iter (int)]
python clusteringEvaluation.py kmeans.out ground_truth.csv
```
